Package io.github.jornegitgud.galaxyquest

Class Tile

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.jornegitgud.galaxyquest.Tile
  • public class Tile
extends java.lang.Object
    this class is used to create all the tiles that make up the galaxy. the tile contains references to other tiles that are above, below left and right from this tile. it has getters and setters.
